Shipping Administrator (RMT/201405/02/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00007643
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
May 2 2014
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Directly responsible for shipping processing.
Co-ordinate packing arrangements with Order Execution Team and Operation Team.
Perform pre-shipment ship to address/end user screening in accordance to ITC.
Prepare all shipment instructions and documentations (Proforma Invoices, Packing Lists and Delivery Notes etc).
Ensure all shipments are timely and delivery schedule is met by working closely with Internal and External teams (such as forwarders).
Ensure proper documentation (COO, LC, GST) are in-place for each delivery/shipment.
Requirements:
Diploma in Business or related discipline.
Sound knowledge of shipping and logistics documentations.
Possess good communication and interpersonal skills.
Able to multi-task in fast pace environment.